    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require lifetime Football Banning Orders for racist football offences",
        "additional_details": "After England\u2019s loss in the Euro 2020 final some of the squad have been subject to racist abuse. This is unacceptable and should not be tolerated under any circumstances. These footballers have played to represent their country yet they are being let down as we aren\u2019t doing enough to protect them, this Government need to do more to protect our players and need to do more to prevent this happening time and time again.",
        "background": "We want to remove racism from football all together. Footballers should not be subject to abuse just because of the colour of their skin and so called fans should not continue to have the privilege of attending games if they contribute towards racism online or in person.",
